advice:
界面上用到结算机构弹出树选择窗口时，即settledeptselected/settledeptselected/checklist.htc的更改方案
.querySelectTree {
	behavior: url ('/ESIM/jsp/epub/settledeptselected/settledeptselected/checklist.htc' );
    .....
}
修改为
.querySelectTree {
	/*behavior: url ('/ESIM/jsp/epub/settledeptselected/settledeptselected/checklist.htc' );*/
	behavior: url(/ECOMM/htc/property.htc);
    .....
}
并在当前界面同名的js资源之前引入
<script language="javascript" src="/ESIM/jsp/epub/settledeptselected/settledeptselected/SettleDeptCheckListPlugin.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

window.showModalDialog替换为sfe.showModalDialog
如果有返回值,例如：
function putInfoFromSubWindow(ret){
if(ret == '1'){
$('BUTTON_NAME').value = $('action').value = '';
xfe.encryt.signform(document.forms[0]);
document.forms[0].submit();
}
}
var ret = window.showModalDialog(url,settings,feature);
putInfoFromSubWindow(ret);
修改为
var rest = sfe.showModalDialog(url,settings,features, putInfoFromSubWindow);

.lastChild.appendChild 改为 sfe.getLastChild 例如  
oRow.parentElement.parentElement.lastChild.appendChild(tmp_tr); 
改为  sfe.getLastChild(oRow.parentElement.parentElement).appendChild(tmp_tr);
